$ Redirection with HTML

code {
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh"
        content="0;
        url=http://renenyffenegger.ch/notes/develeopment/web/HTML/redirection" />
</head></html>
code }

The value of parameter `content` specifies the amount of secunds until the redirection takes place (0 = immediatly).

sa:
  → development/web/HTML/tags/meta

  A 301 redirection can be made on → development/Apache/Server[an Apache Webserver] with an → development/Apache/Server/htaccess[`.htaccess`] file.
